metadata.name: Allegory of Sight and Smell in pepes museum
metadata.description:
Inspired by 'Allegory of Sight and Smell', 1590-1625. Artist: Jan Brueghel the Elder

You see pepe paintings every day but here is a big gallery in front of you.
look at the details. I spent a lot of time in the details to portray a crowded world.
 Hope you enjoy
